video_description: i spent hours walking around in the blazing sun it was my cousins birthday and she decided to go out for breakfast with a group of girls to get a√ßa√≠ bowls i ate a breakfast protein bowl and an a√ßa√≠ bowl i was the only one to get a meal with my a√ßa√≠ bowl but even though i had two things to eati was still hungry they all decided to walk around a bit and chat after two hours of thati was sweating thirsty and hungry so me and my mom decided to leave and go grocery shopping at trader joes after grabbing what we needed we both decided to go out and eat as we were driving looking around we came upon an olive garden my mom reminds me of the stuffed pasta shells they have and i immediately craved them so we went and got a booth and looked over the menu stuffed shells were nowhere to be seen on the menu my heart broke i was excited over nothing the waitress came up to see if we were ready to order for some reason she gave off the weirdest vibe ever idk if i was tripping my mom asked her if they have stuffed shells she said yes i was throbbing in excitement the waitress asked me what sauce i wanted i got confused doesnt it always come with marinara maybe they give options now so i just stuck with marinara do you wanna add a protein to it this is where i was like woah this dish just keeps getting better you can do that i asked in pure confusion she nodded her head so i asked for crispy chicken she takes my moms order and walks away i spend the next minutes munching on breadsticks and salad just picturing how this meal is gonna come out i wonder how will they plate this magnificent meal i never had stuffed shells with all these accommodations i was genuinely excited i see the waitress coming to our table with a tray oh boy my yummy special dish is coming she sets the plate in front of me erm it was nothing that i was expecting she misunderstood and gave me shell shaped pasta with marinara and chicken my high went to an all time low why on earth would i order this no wonder why she was asking me what sauce and protein i wanted imagine if i said just how it is when she asked me if i wanted to add anything she would have brought out plain pasta however no matter how bummed out i was when my dish came i did not speak up about it my mom insisted but i declined cause i just cannot physically say anything or inconvenience someone even if it is not a big deal for them at all i nibbled on my meal and took the rest to go i blamed me not wanting to speak up on the waitresss weird vibe i got but deep down im just very socially awkward i just want stuffed shells someone let me know if they still have it stuffed shells social anxiety olive garden

video_description: i was the only nay on the ohio house resolution on israel it was not an easy decision to make no one wants to vote against a resolution condemning violence but this resolution fell short of what it should have been to condemn terror but to not ignore the damage and destruction endured by the palestinian people i could not vote yes and abandon my palestinian friends and neighbors who for too long had very few stand for them i still strongly pray for the jewish lives lost and mourn with my jewish friends and neighbors as they live through this devastating moment but as my friend rep isaacsohn stated it is not moral equivalence to mourn the loss of all innocent lives including those in gaza i cannot in good conscience sit here and vote yes on a resolution that does not ask for a deescalation of violent retribution launched by israel against largely civilian territory the palestinian children also deserve someone to stand up for them and condemn their murder those babies who right now are denied water electricity and medicine deserve to have someone stand up for them and condemn their abuse an abuse they have suffered for over years with over palestinian lives lost since and thousands more injured and displaced it is time to call for true justice and apply the values of universal human rights to all victims of oppression regardless of nationality religion or skin color i send my prayers for peace and the protection of innocent lives lost during this conflict be it palestinian jewish american or any other loss of life israeli writer gideon levy stated we now have to cry bitterly for the israeli victims but we should also cry for gaza and finally to quote my favorite verse in the quran o you who believe be upholders of justice witnesses for god even though against the interest of yourselves or your parents and kinsmen free palestine

video_description: heres a couple of the many things you could do rather than scrolling through shein or amazon or making that late night walmart and mcdonalds run if youre trying to save money i hope you enjoy this take a nap this is probably the easiest most simple thing you could do it makes time pass by so much more quickly so you dont get those constant intrusive thoughts thatll cost you plus if youve got a history of a bad sleep schedule this would be your opportunity to grab a couple more hours of sleep try yoga i personally have just started practicing yoga and i feel like it helps me a lot i get to wind down calm my mind and stretch my body out i dont know about you but i sleep in some funky positions that leave me cramped up so doing a few stretches throughout the days really helps with those cramps and is a great alternative to working out which i hate to do try a new recipe baking is one of my favorite things to do with friends you dont even have to do any of these alone if you have the basic necessities you could bake or cook a lot of things at home try that frozen chocolate strawberry recipe off tiktok or if youre brave enough try a professional chef tutorial on youtube just for fun clean up your nails im very picky about keeping my nails pretty and clean so it prevents me from wanting to pick at them as an old habit you can paint your nails a pretty color or just simply file them down a bit and clean up your cuticles if youre a perfectionist like me this will keep you occupied for quite some time organize i have a few drawers in my bedroom that i tend to just throw the most random things into so i like to go through it every once and a while and i find some pretty crazy things clean up your desk go through your bookshelf or organize your clothes whatever youve been putting off try it now teach a pet a trick grab some treats and show your dog how to roll over dance in a circle or give a high five if youre a cat person theres a way to teach your cat how to give you a high five watch something find a documentary on netflix thats trending or ask a friend for a movie recommendation i have about different tv shows im in the middle of watching so if you have that habit then make it a goal to finish one of them dance this is a great opportunity to just let yourself lose and calm down and even find a few new songs that pique your interests turn on some s party songs and dance around your room while you get a couple side tasks done lemon diary save money things to do bored fun with friends lemon us lemon follow mariahnichole on
